    "Yet God said He knew Moses by name and he had found favor.",
    "Moses asked to know God’s ways and see His glory.",
    "God said His presence would go with Moses and give him rest.",
    "Moses said if His presence did not go, do not carry them up.",
    "How would it be known he and the people found favor unless God went with them?",
    "God said He would do this also, for Moses had found favor and was known by name.",
    "Moses said, 'Please show me Your glory.'",
